# UITableViewCell.EditingStyle.delete

**Case**

The cell has the delete editing control; this control is a red circle enclosing a minus sign.

## Declaration

```swift
case delete
```

## Constants

- **UITableViewCell.EditingStyle.none**: The cell has no editing control.
- **UITableViewCell.EditingStyle.insert**: The cell has the insert editing control; this control is a green circle enclosing a plus sign.
